creator: Precision Group
descriptionHtml:
The Shore City Shopping Centre app will make your shopping trip faster and easier.

Get access to exclusive offers and rewards with our FREE app. Stay up to date with the latest Shore City news, events and special offers and shop ‘til you drop!

Features:
- Exclusive offers and rewards
- Find out what’s on at the centre
- Be the first to know about special events
- Find centre information including travel, opening times, car parking and more
- Get access to exclusive competitions
- Real-time in centre offer alerts straight to your phone
- Search our shop directory
- View the latest retailer offers

Using the Shore City Shopping Centre app is easy. Create a quick profile to start accessing exclusive offers, competitions, and events now. When you see an offer, tap and present it to the participating shop to redeem it.

Next time you visit Shore City Shopping Centre use our app as your shopping companion.
